{"tid":2387791,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"每次見到人話blue lock 係足球漫畫真係得啖笑","createTime":"2021-01-30T15:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T03:39:25.000Z","uid":199804,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2600a9ee0595fad51310172a73267de9d347e55d","tid":2387791,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T15:02:00.000Z","msg":"應該有唔少人睇<br />\n<br />\n屌你媽 <br />\n<br />\n踢波冇戰術 根本大部分時間係球員輪流1 on 1比技術/身體技能 (好似Pok&eacute;mon咁輪流隻揪)<br />\n又冇左其他足球漫畫必有嘅元素(球隊為勝利團結,詳細講練波+點樣強化球員,不同教練獨有嘅排陣,......)<br />\n仲有一啲經典橋段(離鄉别井,爭正選,屋企人唔比踢,受傷冇得踢,......)都係冇<br />\n<br />\nblue lock 係就係幾好睇 但我就係當普通少年戰鬥漫咁睇 <br />\n叫佢做足球漫畫真係侮辱曬其他足球漫畫 衰啲講連運動漫畫都算不上 根本冇體現到體育精神<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人身同感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37811b510fdf9739256a45f9e6a9dacb1d624d37","tid":2387791,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T15:19:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2f0ef9728eec2ebe0e8ea60c8905591c99f4010","tid":2387791,"uid":347981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T15:40:09.000Z","msg":"1-2"},{"pid":"86badaa1140e455632d3a684c035d02b04ae7f86","tid":2387791,"uid":67505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"不嬲都當超能力漫畫睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有人都係前鋒就預左唔講戰術講1on1對抗<br />\n但畫得真係幾靚，同主角唔係on99大愛型<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2afa8a39814ddcf987dec772c8eecd13b2ec07a3","tid":2387791,"uid":56777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:01:31.000Z","msg":"每次見到人話閃電十一人係足球動畫真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"60033fed8ec067bcc2910aa3af846e8161636e3a","tid":2387791,"uid":56813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"青之葦蘆 好好睇"},{"pid":"7ca8da4e92223d38c724d9ff286c6f855ef37d4b","tid":2387791,"uid":33668,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2600a9ee0595fad51310172a73267de